=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09A planned restructuring at Mitsubishi Motors, a Japanese car co=
mpany that is=20
34% owned by DaimlerChrysler, appeared to go on hold after Mitsubishi agree=
d=20
to bail out its loss-making Australian subsidiary to the tune of A$172m=20
($90m).
=09=09=09=09
