 its purchase of=20
a 16% stake in AT&T Wireless. DoCoMo is keen to promote its third-generatio=
n=20
mobile technology; and AT&T Wireless, which is soon to become a separate=20
company after its parent splits up, needs the cash to pay for bids for=20
American wireless spectrum.
